GiPS code derives directly from OpenGeoTracker Project (http://opengeotracker.org/) by Johan Ekblad (jka@ekblad.org).
Gips is a demo code to manage Direct Marketing campaigns.
GiPS has derived by OpenGeoTracker thanks the contribution by:
	Alessandro Fanna - a.fanna@integraitalia.com
	Luigi Pirelli - luipir@gmail.com
	Davide Rodomonti - davide.friends@gmail.com
GiPS has been released by GPL V2 Licence.
GiPS has released as Fork of the OpenGeoTraker project with consensous of Johan Ekblad. The main reason is the lack of time to merge this projects.

thanks and enjoy the code.
